c colored \u0027boulders\u0027.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sarbian","CreatedById":57146,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-08T11:24:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it is related to\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#fbfbfb;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EModuleAsteroid.\u003C/span\u003EsecondaryRate. Most likely a % chance.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}